metadata.name: No Fun
metadata.description: @fukuball The writing for 8 began at the end of 2015, when the band was putting together Side B of their Trust Fall EP. However, with the @fukuball amount of quality content they were producing, they decided to release an LP instead.[5] Recording took place throughout 2016 and 2017 @fukuball
